Text:"<s2769></s><fArial Black><s1846>NASADIKI</s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<s2769></s><fArial Black><s1846>Nasadiki, ninasadiki.</s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<s2769></s><fArial Black><s1846>Nasadiki kwa Mungu Baba, 
Mwumba wa vyote,</s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<s2769></s><fArial Black><s1846>Nasadiki kwa Yesu Kristu, Mwana wa pekee.</s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<s2769></s><fArial Black><s1846>Nasadiki, ninasadiki. x2</s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<s2769></s><fArial Black><s1846>Kwa uwezo wa Roho Mungu </s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<s2769></s><fArial Black><s1846>katwa-a mwili, Na hapo Bikira Maria kawa mamaye.</s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<s2769></s><fArial Black><s1846>Nasadiki, ninasadiki. x2</s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<s2769></s><fArial Black><s1846>Kwa amri ya Ponsyo Pilato kasulibiwa,</s></f>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<s2769></s><fArial Black><s1846>Akafa, ‘kazikwa, akashukia kuzimu.</s></f>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<s2769></s><fArial Black><s1846>Nasadiki, ninasadiki. x2</s></f>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<s2769></s><fArial Black><s1846>Siku ya tatu kafufuka, kapaa mbinguni,</s></f>"},{ID:20,
Text:"<s2769></s><fArial Black><s1846>Kaketi kuume kwa Mungu, 
Baba Mwenyezi.</s></f>"},{ID:20,
Text:"<s2769></s><fArial Black><s1846>Nasadiki, ninasadiki. x2</s></f>"},{ID:21,
Text:"<s2769></s><fArial Black><s1846>Atarudi siku ya mwisho kutuhukumu.</s></f>"},{ID:22,
Text:"<s2769></s><fArial Black><s1846>Nasadiki kwa Roho Mfariji Mtakatifu.</s></f>"},{ID:22,
Text:"<s2769></s><fArial Black><s1846>Nasadiki, ninasadiki. x2</s></f>"},{ID:23,
Text:"<s2769></s><fArial Black><s1846>Kanisa pia, takatifu na katoliki;</s></f>"},{ID:24,
Text:"<s2769></s><fArial Black><s1846>Ushirika wa watakatifu wa mbinguni.</s></f>"},{ID:24,
Text:"<s2769></s><fArial Black><s1846>Nasadiki, ninasadiki. x2</s></f>"},{ID:25,
Text:"<s2769></s><fArial Black><s1846>Na maondoleo ya dhambi kwa ubatizo;</s></f>"},{ID:26,
Text:"<s2769></s><fArial Black><s1846>‘fufuko wa mi-ili, uzima wa milele.</s></f>"},{ID:26,
Text:"<s2769></s><fArial Black><s1846>Nasadiki, ninasadiki. x2</s></f>"},{ID:13,
