Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>UTUKUFU</s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Utukufu kwa Mungu juu mbinguni, Na amani iwe </s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>kwa watu wenye Mapenzi mema duniani kote.</s></f>"},{ID:15,
