Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Imbeni aleluya, aleluya imbeni shangwe kwa Bwana Yesu ndiye mweza wetu </s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Dunia i karibu, Bwana siniache Na mengi majaribu yapo pande zote </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Siku zote adui ni ndani na nje Bwana Yesu nivute karibu na wewe </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Imbeni aleluya, aleluya imbeni shangwe kwa Bwana Yesu ndiye mweza wetu </s></f>"},{ID:5,
