Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Nena kunihimiza au kunionya, Nena nikusikie mwenye kuniponya </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Imbeni aleluya, aleluya imbeni shangwe kwa Bwana Yesu ndiye mweza wetu </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Umewapa ahadi wakufuatao 
Kwenda uliko wewe, Wawe huko nao </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Nami nimeahidi kukutumikia Nipe neema, Bwana, yakukwandamia </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Imbeni aleluya, aleluya imbeni shangwe kwa Bwana Yesu ndiye mweza wetu </s></f>"},{ID:9,
